    "# Example of spatial multi-omics data (mouse brain with Parkinson's disease)"
   ]
  },

    "import os\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import scanpy as sc\n",
    "import squidpy as sq\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "import metachat as mc"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# setting work dictionary\n",
    "os.chdir(\"/home/Project/MetaChat_test/mouse_brain\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Data preprocessing"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Preprocessing for transcriptomics data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "AnnData object with n_obs × n_vars = 3011 × 32285\n",
       "    obs: 'in_tissue', 'array_row', 'array_col'\n",
       "    var: 'gene_ids', 'feature_types', 'genome'\n",
       "    uns: 'spatial'\n",
       "    obsm: 'spatial'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 3,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "adata_RNA = sc.read_h5ad('data/multiomics_mousebrain_parkinson_RNA.h5ad')\n",
    "adata_RNA"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "adata_RNA.var_names_make_unique()\n",
    "adata_RNA.raw = adata_RNA\n",
    "sc.pp.normalize_total(adata_RNA, inplace=True)\n",
    "sc.pp.log1p(adata_RNA)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "adata_visual = adata_RNA.copy()\n",
    "random_seed = 42\n",
    "sc.pp.highly_variable_genes(adata_visual, min_mean=0.0125, max_mean=10, min_disp=0.2)\n",
    "adata_visual = adata_visual[:, adata_visual.var.highly_variable]\n",
    "sc.tl.pca(adata_visual, svd_solver='arpack', random_state=random_seed)\n",
    "sc.pp.neighbors(adata_visual, n_neighbors=10, n_pcs=40, random_state=random_seed)\n",
    "sc.tl.umap(adata_visual, random_state=random_seed)\n",
    "sc.tl.leiden(adata_visual, resolution=1)\n",
    "sc.pl.spatial(adata_visual, color='leiden')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cluster_to_cell_type = {\n",
    "    '0': 'Striatum dorsal region',\n",
    "    '1': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "    '2': 'Striatum ventral region',\n",
    "    '3': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "    '4': 'Lateral septal complex',\n",
    "    '5': 'Fiber tracts',\n",
    "    '6': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "    '7': 'Fiber tracts',\n",
    "    '8': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "    '9': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "    '10': 'Striatum dorsal region',\n",
    "    '11': 'Striatum ventral region',\n",
    "    '12': 'Ventricular systems',\n",
    "    '13': 'Cerebral cortex',\n",
    "}\n",
    "adata_RNA.obs['tissue_type'] = adata_visual.obs['leiden'].map(cluster_to_cell_type)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 500x500 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize = (5,5))\n",
    "sq.pl.spatial_scatter(adata = adata_RNA,\n",
    "                      color = \"tissue_type\",\n",
    "                      ax = ax)\n",
    "ax.set_box_aspect(1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Preprocessing for metabolomics data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "AnnData object with n_obs × n_vars = 3011 × 3015\n",
       "    obs: 'orig.ident', 'nCount_RNA', 'nFeature_RNA'\n",
       "    var: 'features'\n",
       "    uns: 'spatial'\n",
       "    obsm: 'spatial'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "adata_MSI = sc.read_h5ad('data/multiomics_mousebrain_parkinson_MSI.h5ad')\n",
    "adata_MSI.uns['spatial'] = adata_RNA.uns['spatial']\n",
    "adata_MSI.obsm['spatial'] = adata_RNA.obsm['spatial']\n",
    "adata_MSI"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "adata_MSI.var_names_make_unique()\n",
    "adata_RNA.raw = adata_RNA\n",
    "sc.pp.normalize_total(adata_MSI, inplace=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Combine the transcriptomics and metabolomics data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from scipy.sparse import hstack\n",
    "X_combined = hstack([adata_RNA.X, adata_MSI.X])\n",
    "X_combined = X_combined.tocsr()\n",
    "var_combined = pd.DataFrame({\"features\" : np.concatenate((np.array(adata_RNA.var_names),np.array(adata_MSI.var_names)))})\n",
    "var_combined.index = var_combined[\"features\"]\n",
    "adata = sc.AnnData(X_combined, obs=adata_RNA.obs, var=var_combined)\n",
    "adata.obsm = adata_RNA.obsm\n",
    "adata.uns = adata_RNA.uns"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## MCC Inference"
   ]
  },
  {

   "metadata": {},

    "### Constructing group-level MCC"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "mc.tl.communication_group(adata = adata,\n",
    "                          database_name = 'MetaChatDB',\n",
    "                          group_name = \"tissue_type\",\n",
    "                          sum_metabolites = sum_metabolites,\n",
    "                          n_permutations = 100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<div>\n",
       "<style scoped>\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n",
       "        vertical-align: middle;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n",
       "        vertical-align: top;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "\n",
       "    .dataframe thead th {\n",
       "        text-align: right;\n",
       "    }\n",
       "</style>\n",
       "<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n",
       "  <thead>\n",
       "    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n",
       "      <th></th>\n",
       "      <th>Cerebral cortex</th>\n",
       "      <th>Fiber tracts</th>\n",
       "      <th>Lateral septal complex</th>\n",
       "      <th>Striatum dorsal region</th>\n",
       "      <th>Striatum ventral region</th>\n",
       "      <th>Ventricular systems</th>\n",
       "    </tr>\n",
       "  </thead>\n",
       "  <tbody>\n",
       "    <tr>\n",
